Al White https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Al_White 0 Allen "Al" White (born May 17, 1942) is an American character actor. He has appeared in various movies, such as Airplane! and Airplane II: The Sequel, and Back to the Future Part II. Over the course of his Hollywood acting career, White has frequently portrayed police detectives in television and film. Allen_"_Al_"_White ( born May_17_,_1942 ) is an_American_character_actor .
